							<p>In Nostr, users sign their posts with their cryptographic keys. This cryptographic signature ensures the authenticity of your data. You can prove what you did (and did not) create. Each client validates these signatures, ensuring data integrity. User-selected relays store and send data. These relays communicate directly with other users, with no stops between.</p>
